    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "艾玛马上跟在希罗身后，来到过道上。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Ema",
        "appearance": [
          "Surprised1",
          "ArmR3"
        ],
        "position": 50
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "等、等我一下，希罗！",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv05/0101Adv05_Ema001.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "过道上又出现了\n许多名少女。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "少女们的视线都集中在了艾玛身上。\n除了希罗，艾玛并未见过这些少女。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Ema",
        "appearance": [
          "Normal1",
          "ArmR3"
        ],
        "position": 50
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "（太好了……我还在想，\n 要是全部人都是初中的同学，我该怎么办呢……）",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv05/0101Adv05_Ema002.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "但，所有人的年纪看起来都和自己差不多。\n跟艾玛和希罗一样，她们都身穿奇妙的衣裳。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "而过道前方，一个黑衣异形正在走动着。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "（那个异形就是所谓的看守吧）",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv05/0101Adv05_Ema003.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "其他少女也吓得脸色煞白，不知所措，\n只好跟随看守开始移动。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "希罗远远走在了艾玛前边。\n艾玛小跑着追赶着她。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Ema",
        "appearance": [
          "Surprised1",
          "ArmR1"
        ],
        "position": 50
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "希罗！",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv05/0101Adv05_Ema004.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "hideChars"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Hiro",
        "appearance": [
          "Pensive1"
        ],
        "position": 30
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Ema",
        "appearance": [
          "Normal1",
          "ArmR3"
        ],
        "position": 70
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "……",
      "speaker": "二阶堂希罗",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv05/0101Adv05_Hiro001.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "听、听我说。虽然发生了这样那样的事，\n不过还能见到希罗你，真是太好了。",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv05/0101Adv05_Ema005.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "我已经下决心改变了，\n已经不是过去的我了。\n我想和你做朋友。",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv05/0101Adv05_Ema006.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "……",
      "speaker": "二阶堂希罗",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv05/0101Adv05_Hiro002.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "希罗似乎决意要无视艾玛，\n没有放慢脚步。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Ema",
        "appearance": [
          "Surprised1",
          "ArmR3"
        ],
        "position": 70
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "我，我不会放弃的！",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv05/0101Adv05_Ema007.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Hiro",
        "appearance": [
          "Angry1"
        ],
        "position": 30
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "……",
      "speaker": "二阶堂希罗",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv05/0101Adv05_Hiro003.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "希罗发出咬牙切齿的声音，\n转过身来面向艾玛。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Hiro",
        "appearance": [
          "Angry1"
        ],
        "position": 40
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "然后，毫不犹豫的推了艾玛一下。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Ema",
        "appearance": [
          "Surprised1",
          "ArmR3"
        ],
        "position": 80
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "呀！",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv05/0101Adv05_Ema008.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "sfx",
      "params": {
        "path": "/Audio/SFX/Scenario/Sfx_Scenario_006 Fall down.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "hide",
      "params": {
        "id": "Ema"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "艾玛当即摔倒在地，\n膝盖擦在坚硬的石地板上。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Hiro",
        "appearance": [
          "Angry1"
        ],
        "position": 50
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "而动手伤人的希罗\n正恶狠狠地俯视着艾玛。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "你改变了，\n跟我有什么关系？",
      "speaker": "二阶堂希罗",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv05/0101Adv05_Hiro004.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "我讨厌你的事实不会改变。\n永远不会。",
      "speaker": "二阶堂希罗",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv05/0101Adv05_Hiro005.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "hideChars"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "希罗凶巴巴地说道，\n然后转身离去。"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Ema",
        "appearance": [
          "Surprised1",
          "ArmR3"
        ],
        "position": 50
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "等、等下……！",
      "speaker": "樱羽艾玛",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv05/0101Adv05_Ema009.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "hideChars"
    },
    {
      "type": "command",
      "command": "char",
      "params": {
        "id": "Sherry",
        "appearance": [
          "Pensive1",
          "ArmL4",
          "ArmR2"
        ],
        "position": 50
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "唔……",
      "speaker": "???",
      "voice": "/Audio/Voice/Act01_Chapter01/Act01_Chapter01_Adv05/0101Adv05_Unknown001.ogg"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "一位水蓝色头发的少女，正兴致勃勃的观察着二人。"
    },
